detaileddescription.para: implemented in terms of the default density $ p(t) $ as \[S(t) = 1 - \int_0^t p(\tau) d\tau. \]

simplesect.para: This default implementation uses numerical integration, which might be inefficient and inaccurate. Derived classes should override it if a more efficient implementation is available.
